data.description: This Fischer Masterpiece Designer Home is perfect if you are looking for all the bells and whistles.  The main floor boasts a spacious open kitchen with an oversized island and high-end finishes, a family room with a stunning stone fireplace, living room, dining area, and a keeping room. The upper-level private owner's retreat, complete with a sitting area, a spa-like bathroom, and a walk-in closet, is just a few steps away. The laundry room is conveniently located between the owner's retreat and the three spacious bedrooms. There's also an open-concept loft theater room/play area for everyone to enjoy! This beautiful home sits on a private 1/2 acre level corner lot with a side-entry garage and is conveniently located near schools, shopping, restaurants, and more. Come see this immaculate home today and write a contract tonight!
